title: Large Two Bedroom Apartment In Missouri City, Tour Today!
posting_body: ['Plantation at Quail Valley:', 'The Savannah...', 'You Deserve the Best!', '2815 Cypress Point Dr,', 'Missouri City, TX 77459', '$1,595/mo/', 'THIS IS OUR LARGEST UNIT!', 'MUST SEE TO APPRECIATE...', 'KEY FEATURES', 'Sq Footage: 1072 sq ft.', 'Elevators in each building', 'Bedrooms: 2 Bedrooms', 'Bathrooms: 2 Baths', 'Parking:  Off street | Guest parking', 'Lease Duration: 1 Year (See Details Below)', 'Deposit: $350', 'Pets Policy: Cats & Dogs OK', 'Laundry: Connections In Unit', 'Property Type: Apartment', 'DESCRIPTION', 'Plantation at Quail Valley is a unique independent-living community that provides affordable, but luxurious, apartment homes for those 55 years and better.', 'Nestled in a quiet residential neighborhood, it offers a wide menu of services and amenities for active seniors.', 'Residents can relax on their private patios and balconies that overlook beautiful courtyards.', 'Transportation, meals, trips, classes and a wide variety of social activities are available at your choice.', 'RENTAL FEATURES', 'Living room', 'Walk-in closet', 'Master bath', 'Storage space', 'Range / Oven', 'Refrigerator', 'Dishwasher', 'Microwave', 'Garbage disposal', 'Balcony, Deck, or Patio', 'Air conditioning', 'Ceiling fans', 'Cable-ready', 'COMMUNITY FEATURES', 'Over 55 active community', 'Elevator', 'Controlled access', 'Gated entry', 'Shared pool', 'Fitness center', 'Clubhouse', 'Business center', 'Guest parking', 'Off-street parking', 'On-street parking', 'LEASE TERMS', 'Call and ask us about our current special--$599 Total move in!', 'ADDITIONAL LINKS', 'Website: <URL>', 'Virtual Tour: <URL>', 'Contact info:', 'Sandra Mendez', 'ParaWest Management', 'show contact info']
